data.description: Excellent opportunity to own a great condominium in Kaneohe! Great 2 bedroom 1 bath in the Windward Estates subdivision! Enjoy this breezy and spacious unit. 2 Lanais! One lanai in the living room and another in the bedroom! Great mountain views, cool atmosphere and a very walkable environment. Washer and Dryer in the unit. 2 parking spaces available! Very rare opportunity to own at the Mountain View Terrace condominiums. Make this condo your new home! Easy to show, move in ready. Pets allowed with ESA Certification. Elevator services all floors. Recreational facilities include half court basketball court, volleyball court and swimming pool! Seller motivated. All offers considered.
